  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      There is association between Hepatitis C and Parkinson's Disease as shown from previous
      studies. The clinical profile and natural history is not fully studied yet. We aim at
      studying the clinical characteristics of Parkinson's Disease in patients with hepatitis C
      infection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
