    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient with history of Parkinson's Disease and Hepatitis C infection.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Advanced liver cirrhosis.

          -  Patients with hepatic failure.

          -  Symptoms of Parkinson's plus syndrome.
      </textblock>
